Q_DESC:
To write a program in which the user has to perform operations in a linked list.
The user has to input a set of elements into an array. Now the arrays elements are taken to form a linked list. Now the task is to perform bubble sort in the linked list. 
INPUT:
90 1 11 2 56 12//linked list
OUTPUT:
Linked list before sorting 
12 56 2 11 1 90 
Linked list after sorting 
1 2 11 12 56 90
TESTCASE_1:
90 1 11 2 56 12
###---###SEPERATOR---###---
Linked list before sorting 
12 56 2 11 1 90 
Linked list after sorting 
1 2 11 12 56 90
